content.rendered: The Chennai-based team of TTE Engineering recently enjoyed a day-long team-building event held at a beach resort at Mahabalipuram, Tamil Nadu. Amidst a landscape of lush greenery, they participated in fun group activities that required communication, teamwork and coordination with each other. Apart from that, they also enjoyed some outdoor sports activities like beach volleyball, cricket, table tennis and archery. Rahul Kalra, VP of TTE Engineering was part of the event and discussed the team’s collective goals and plans for the future, over a leisurely lunch and tea break. It was a fun and refreshing break from their daily routine.
